<script type="text/javascript" async="true">
(function() {
  var host = window.location.hostname;
  var element = document.createElement('script');
  var firstScript = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0];
  var url = 'https://cmp.quantcast.com'
    .concat('/choice/', 'LBBrF-bdAtkuF', '/', host, '/choice.js?tag_version=V2');
  var uspTries = 0;
  var uspTriesLimit = 3;
  element.async = true;
  element.type = 'text/javascript';
  element.src = url;

  firstScript.parentNode.insertBefore(element, firstScript);

  function makeStub() {
    var TCF_LOCATOR_NAME = '__tcfapiLocator';
    var queue = [];
    var win = window;
    var cmpFrame;

    function addFrame() {
      var doc = win.document;
      var otherCMP = !!(win.frames[TCF_LOCATOR_NAME]);

      if (!otherCMP) {
        if (doc.body) {
          var iframe = doc.createElement('iframe');

          iframe.style.cssText = 'display:none';
          iframe.name = TCF_LOCATOR_NAME;
          doc.body.appendChild(iframe);
        } else {
          setTimeout(addFrame, 5);
        }
      }
      return !otherCMP;
    }

    function tcfAPIHandler() {
      var gdprApplies;
      var args = arguments;

      if (!args.length) {
        return queue;
      } else if (args[0] === 'setGdprApplies') {
        if (
          args.length > 3 &&
          args[2] === 2 &&
          typeof args[3] === 'boolean'
        ) {
          gdprApplies = args[3];
          if (typeof args[2] === 'function') {
            args[2]('set', true);
          }
        }
      } else if (args[0] === 'ping') {
        var retr = {
          gdprApplies: gdprApplies,
          cmpLoaded: false,
          cmpStatus: 'stub'
        };

        if (typeof args[2] === 'function') {
          args[2](retr);
        }
      } else {
        if(args[0] === 'init' && typeof args[3] === 'object') {
          args[3] = Object.assign(args[3], { tag_version: 'V2' });
        }
        queue.push(args);
      }
    }

    function postMessageEventHandler(event) {
      var msgIsString = typeof event.data === 'string';
      var json = {};

      try {
        if (msgIsString) {
          json = JSON.parse(event.data);
        } else {
          json = event.data;
        }
      } catch (ignore) {}

      var payload = json.__tcfapiCall;

      if (payload) {
        window.__tcfapi(
          payload.command,
          payload.version,
          function(retValue, success) {
            var returnMsg = {
              __tcfapiReturn: {
                returnValue: retValue,
                success: success,
                callId: payload.callId
              }
            };
            if (msgIsString) {
              returnMsg = JSON.stringify(returnMsg);
            }
            if (event && event.source && event.source.postMessage) {
              event.source.postMessage(returnMsg, '*');
            }
          },
          payload.parameter
        );
      }
    }

    while (win) {
      try {
        if (win.frames[TCF_LOCATOR_NAME]) {
          cmpFrame = win;
          break;
        }
      } catch (ignore) {}

      if (win === window.top) {
        break;
      }
      win = win.parent;
    }
    if (!cmpFrame) {
      addFrame();
      win.__tcfapi = tcfAPIHandler;
      win.addEventListener('message', postMessageEventHandler, false);
    }
  };

  makeStub();

  var uspStubFunction = function() {
    var arg = arguments;
    if (typeof window.__uspapi !== uspStubFunction) {
      setTimeout(function() {
        if (typeof window.__uspapi !== 'undefined') {
          window.__uspapi.apply(window.__uspapi, arg);
        }
      }, 500);
    }
  };

  var checkIfUspIsReady = function() {
    uspTries++;
    if (window.__uspapi === uspStubFunction && uspTries < uspTriesLimit) {
      console.warn('USP is not accessible');
    } else {
      clearInterval(uspInterval);
    }
  };

  if (typeof window.__uspapi === 'undefined') {
    window.__uspapi = uspStubFunction;
    var uspInterval = setInterval(checkIfUspIsReady, 6000);
  }
})();
</script>

        <style>
    #hidden-url {position: absolute; left: 65px; top: 2px; display: none; padding: 2px 6px 4px 6px; background: #fdcc1a; margin-top: 5px; width: 485px; border-radius: 5px; animation-duration: .3s; z-index: 100;}
    #hidden-url input{ font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; outline: none; border: 1px solid #DDDDDD; border-radius: 5px; padding: 8px 4px; width: 435px; margin-left: 5px; font-family: monospace;}
    #hidden-url .hide-url {cursor: pointer; font-size: 22px; margin: 0 5px; color: #000; vertical-align: middle;}
    #copy-clipboard {position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 31px; padding: 2px 6px; background: #fdcc1a; margin-top: 5px; animation-duration: .3s; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; width: 200px; cursor: pointer; padding-left: 15px;}
</style>

<script>

    function hideOnClick( ){
        $(document).click(function(event) {
            if(!$(event.target).closest('.hd-sh-wrapper').length && !$(event.target).closest('#hidden-url').length) {
                if($('.hd-sh-wrapper').is(":visible")) {
                    //$('.hidden-share-wrapper').hide();
                    $('.sh-header').trigger('click');
                }
            }
        });
    }

    $(function() {
        $('.hd-sh-wrapper').bind('animationEnd oAnimationEnd msAnimationEnd mozAnimationEnd webkitAnimationEnd', function(event){
            if(  $(event.target).hasClass('nkoout') )
            {
                $('.hd-sh-wrapper').hide();
            }

        });

        $('#sh-pos-abs').toggle( function(){
                $('.sh-header').addClass('clicked');
                $('.hd-sh-wrapper').removeClass('nkoout').addClass('nkoin').show();
            }, function(){
                $('.hd-sh-wrapper').removeClass('nkoin').addClass('nkoout');

                $('.main-sh').removeClass('clicked');
                if( $('#hidden-url').is(":visible") ) {
                    $('#copy-to-clip').click();
                }
        });

        var pathname = encodeURI('https://www.filmaffinity.com/es/topgen.php?genres=&chv=0&orderby=avg&movietype=movie%7C&country=&fromyear=2013&toyear=2023&ratingcount=3&runtimemin=0&runtimemax=4');
        var slideOptions = { direction: 'left' };

        $('#copy-to-clip').toggle(
            function(){
                $('#hidden-url').show();

                    $('#hidden-url').find(':input').val(pathname);
                    //$('#hidden-url').find(':input').select();
                    var text = $('#hidden-url').find(':input').text();
            },
            function(){
                    $('#hidden-url').hide();
        });

        $('#hidden-url').on('click', '#copy-clipboard', function(){
            $(this).text( $('#copy-clipboard').attr('data-text') );
            navigator.clipboard.writeText( pathname )
                .then(() => {
                    console.log( pathname );
            }).catch(err => {
                    console.error('Could not copy text: ', err);
            });
        })

        $('#hidden-url').find('.hide-url').click(function()
        {
            $('#copy-to-clip').trigger('click')
        });

        hideOnClick();
    });
</script>

    $('#load-more-bt').click(function(){

        $('#load-more-bt').hide();
        $('#loading').show();

        $.ajax({url: location.href,
                data: {from: tmFrom + tmPageSize, paramGrid: configGrid, orderby: configGrid.orderby, showHeader: parseInt($('.header-pg').length)},
                type: "POST",
                dataType: 'html',
        }).done(function( html ) {

            $('#loading').hide();

            //$('#top-movies').append(html);
            //$('.poster-list-grid').last().insertAfter(html);
            if( $('.poster-list-grid').length >  0){
                var html = $('<ul class="poster-list-grid">'+ html +'</ul>');
                $(html).insertAfter('.poster-list-grid:last');
            } else {
                $('#top-movies').append(html);
            }

            tmFrom += tmPageSize;

            if(tmFrom + tmPageSize >= tmResCount)
            {
                $('#load-more-div').remove();
            }
            else
            {
                $('#load-more-bt').show();
            }


        });

    });


    $('body').on('click', function (e) {
        if ($(e.target).data('toggle') !== 'popover'
            && $(e.target).parents('.popover.in').length === 0) {
            $('.popover').popover('dispose');
        }

    $('.z-top-movies #top-movies').on('click', '.providers', function()
    {
        var cell = $(this).closest('li');
        var movieId = $('.movie-card', cell).attr('data-movie-id');

        var button = $(this);

        var params = {
            action: 'getOffers',
            movieId: movieId,
        };

        $.post(pageUrl('movies.ajax.php'), params, function(data)
        {
            var offers = $(data.offers);
            offersTitle = $('.title', offers).text();

            $('.title', offers).remove();

            offersCache[movieId] = offers;

            loadOffersPopover(button, movieId);
        });


    })

    $('#fromyear').selectpicker();

    $('.fframe').on('submit', 'form', function(event)
    {
            var submitUrl = pageUrl('topgen.php');
        if(flagAdm > 0)
            submitUrl = pageUrl('adm/topgen.php');

        event.preventDefault();

        updateFlagsFilter();

        var platformsSelect = $('.nav.nav-tabs li').map(function(idx, elem) {
            if( $(elem).hasClass('selected') )
                return parseInt($(elem).attr('data-prov-id'));
        }).get();

        $('input[name="platforms"]').val(platformsSelect );

        processedForm = filter2request( $('#filter_top').serializeArray() );

        if( parseInt(processedForm.fromyear) > parseInt(processedForm.toyear) ){
            var faNoty = FaNoty.getInstance();
            faNoty.show('error', tcCommon.t('Error top years'), {layout: 'center'});
        } else {
            $.ajax({
                method: "GET",
                url: submitUrl,
                data: processedForm,
            })
            .done(function( msg ) {
               location.assign( submitUrl );
            });
        }
    })
    .on('click', '.reset-filter', function()
    {
        loadFilter(defaultFilter);

        $('#fromyear').selectpicker('val', defaultFilter.fromYear.toString());
        $('#toyear').selectpicker('val', defaultFilter.toYear.toString());
        $('input[name="orderby"]').val('avg');
        
    })

    $('.genre-combo').on('hide.bs.dropdown', '.dropdown', function (e)
    {
        if(e.clickEvent != undefined && $(e.clickEvent.target).closest('.dropdown-item').length > 0)
        {
            e.preventDefault();
        }
    })

    .on('click', '.close-combo', function()
    {
        $(this).closest('.dropdown').find('.dropdown-toggle').dropdown('toggle');
    })

    .on('click', '.reset-combo', function()
    {
        let menu = $(this).closest('.dropdown-menu');

        $.each($('input:checked', menu), function(index, checkedInput)
        {
            setGenreCheck($(checkedInput).closest('label'), false);

        });

        menu.find('.include').removeClass('include');
        menu.find('.exclude').removeClass('exclude');

        renderGenresLegend();
    })


    .on('click', 'label', function(e)
    {
        e.preventDefault();

        let label = $(this);
        let input = $('input', label);
        let group = label.closest('.btn-group');


        //Aqui se hace click en el texto
        if(!input.prop('disabled'))
        {
            let toCheck = !input.is(':checked');

            $.each($('input:checked', group), function(index, checkedInput)
            {
                setGenreCheck($(checkedInput).closest('label'), false);
            });

            if(toCheck)
            {
                setGenreCheck(label, true);
                toggleClass( group, label );
            }else{
                toggleClass( group, label );
            }
        }
        else
        {
            //toggleClass( group, label );
            //Aqui se hace click en alguna de las aspas
            if($('input:checked', group).length == 0)
            {
                //si no hay nada marcado, incluimos
                $('label:eq(0)', group).trigger('click');
            }
            else if($('input:checked', group).index() == 0)
            {
                //si está marcado el incluir, marcamos el excluir
                $('label:eq(2)', group).trigger('click');
            }
            else
            {
                $.each($('input:checked', group), function(index, checkedInput)
                {
                    setGenreCheck($(checkedInput).closest('label'), false);
                });
            }
        }

        //renderLegend();
        renderGenresLegend();

    })

    //Si pulsan en algunos de los check, hay que poner disabled el valor del genre-combo
    $('.flags-content').on('click', 'div[data-flag="movie"] .fa-btn-checkbox, div[data-flag="serie"] .fa-btn-checkbox, div[data-flag="documentary"] .fa-btn-checkbox', function(e){
        if(!$(this).hasClass('disabled')){
            if( $(this).find('input').attr('data-option') == 'ex-anim' && $(this).hasClass('active')){
                $('.genre-combo .dropdown-item[data-value="AN"]').removeClass('disabled');
            } else if($(this).find('input').attr('data-option') == 'ex-anim') {
                $('.genre-combo .dropdown-item[data-value="AN"]').addClass('disabled');
            }

            if( $(this).find('input').attr('data-option') == 'ex-docu' && $(this).hasClass('active')){
                $('.genre-combo .dropdown-item[data-value="DO"]').removeClass('disabled');
            } else if($(this).find('input').attr('data-option') == 'ex-docu') {
                $('.genre-combo .dropdown-item[data-value="DO"]').addClass('disabled');
            }

            if( $(this).find('input').attr('data-option') == 'ex-serie' && $(this).hasClass('active')){
                $('.genre-combo .dropdown-item[data-value="TV_SE"]').removeClass('disabled');
            } else if($(this).find('input').attr('data-option') == 'ex-serie'){
                $('.genre-combo .dropdown-item[data-value="TV_SE"]').addClass('disabled');
            }

        }
    })

    //Si pulsan en algunos de genre-combo, disabled el check

            $('.flags-content .fa-btn-checkbox input[data-option="ex-anim"]').closest('.fa-btn-checkbox').addClass('disabled');

        if( !$(this).hasClass('disabled') && $(this).attr('data-value') == 'TV_SE' ){

            $('.flags-content .fa-btn-checkbox input[data-option="ex-anim"]').closest('.fa-btn-checkbox').removeClass('disabled');
        }

        if( $(this).closest('.btn-group').find('.active').length == 0 && $(this).attr('data-value') == 'DO'){
            $('.flags-content .fa-btn-checkbox input[data-option="ex-docu"]').closest('.fa-btn-checkbox').removeClass('disabled');
        }

        if( $(this).closest('.btn-group').find('.active').length == 0 && $(this).attr('data-value') == 'TV_SE'){
            $('.flags-content .fa-btn-checkbox input[data-option="ex-serie"]').closest('.fa-btn-checkbox').removeClass('disabled');
        }

    });

    $('.country-combo').on('click', '.bootstrap-select', function(){
        var ulList = $(this).find('.dropdown-menu ul li');

        ulList.each(function(index, value){
            var wrapper = $(value).find('.flag-wrapper'),
            countryId = $(wrapper).attr('id');
            if( typeof countryId != 'undefined'){
                countryId = countryId.substr(0,2);
                var src = $('select#country option[value="'+ countryId + '"]').attr('data-style');
                $(value).find('.flag-wrapper').html( src );
            }

        })

    })

    $('a[href*=#].up-button').click(function() {
        $('html,body').animate({scrollTop:'0px'}, 150);
        return false;
    });


    function setGenreCheck(label, value)
    {
        if(value)
        {
            label.addClass('active');
        }
        else
        {
            label.removeClass('active');
        }

        $('input', label).prop('checked', value);
    }

    function setGenreState(labelText, genre)
    {
        var state = genre.substr(0,1);
        if( state == '+' )
        {
            labelText.addClass('include');
        }
        else if( state == '-' )
        {
            labelText.addClass('exclude');
        }
    }

    function toggleClass( group, clicklabel )
    {
        let label = group.find('.text');

        if( label.hasClass('include') ){
            if( clicklabel.find('.fa-check').length == 0 )
                label.removeClass('include').addClass('exclude');
            else
                label.removeClass('include');

        }else if( label.hasClass('exclude') ){

            label.removeClass('exclude');

            if( clicklabel.find('.fa-check').length > 0 ){
                label.addClass('include');
            }

        }else{

            if( clicklabel.find('.fa-times').length > 0 )
                label.addClass('exclude');
            else if( clicklabel.find('.fa-check').length > 0 )
                label.addClass('include');

        }
    }

    function setFlag(label, status)
    {
        if(status)
        {            
            label.addClass('active');
        }
        else
        {
            label.removeClass('active');
        }

        $('input', label).prop('checked', status);

    }


    function updateFlagsFilter()
    {
        var flagType = $('[name="flags-type"]').val();

        var options = new Array();


        var flagOptions = $('.flags-content [data-flag="' + flagType + '"] input');
        $.each(flagOptions, function(index, input)
        {
            if($(input).prop('checked'))
            {
                options.push($(input).attr('data-option'));
            }
        });

        var flagFilter = flagType + '|' + options.join(':');


        $('.fframe [name="movietype"]').val(flagFilter);

    }

    function loadFilterSliders(gen_filter)
    {
        if(gen_filter.runtime[0] == undefined)
            gen_filter.runtime[0] = defaultFilter.runtimeMin;

        if(gen_filter.runtime[1] == undefined)
            gen_filter.runtime[1] = defaultFilter.runtimeMax;

        $('#filter_top .flags-slider').find('.sliderratings').slider({
            ticks: [20, 100, 500, 1000],
            ticks_labels: ['+20', '+100', '+500', '+1000'],
            ticks_positions: [0, 33, 66, 100],
            min: 20,
            lock_to_ticks: true,
        }).slider('setValue', gen_filter.minRatingCount);

        if( $('#filter_top .flags-slider').find('.sliderruntime').slider().length > 0 )
            $('#filter_top .flags-slider').find('.sliderruntime').slider('destroy');

        var flagTypeSel = $('select[name="flags-type"]').val();

        $('#filter_top .flags-slider').find('.sliderruntime').slider({
            ticks: flagsConfig[flagTypeSel].sliderruntime.ticks,
            ticks_labels: flagsConfig[flagTypeSel].sliderruntime.labels,
            ticks_positions: flagsConfig[flagTypeSel].sliderruntime.positions,
            lock_to_ticks: true,
            range: true,
        }).slider('setValue', gen_filter.runtime);
    }

    function filter2request( arrayForm ){

        var request = {};
        request.genres = new Array();

        for( i = 0; i < arrayForm.length; i++ ){
            switch( arrayForm[i].name ){
                case 'country':
                    request.country = arrayForm[i].value;
                break;
                case 'fromyear':
                    request.fromyear = parseInt(arrayForm[i].value);
                break;
                case 'toyear':
                    request.toyear = parseInt(arrayForm[i].value);
                break;
                case 'minRatingCount':
                    var ratingCount = convertValueRatCount( arrayForm[i].value );
                    request.ratingcount = ratingCount;
                break;
                case 'sliderruntime':
                    var ratCount = convertValueRuntime( arrayForm[i].value );
                    request.runtimemin = ratCount.runtimeMin;
                    request.runtimemax = ratCount.runtimeMax;
                break;
                case 'platforms':
                    if( arrayForm[i].value !== '')
                        request.platforms = arrayForm[i].value.split(',');
                break;
                case 'genres[]':
                    request.genres.push(arrayForm[i].value);
                break;
                case 'movietype':
                    request.movietype = arrayForm[i].value;
                break;
                case 'chv':
                    request.chv = arrayForm[i].value;
                break;
                case 'orderby':
                    request.orderby = arrayForm[i].value;
                break;
                default:
                    console.log('default');
            }
        }

        //transforma un array en string separado por comas
        request.genres = request.genres.join();

        return request;
    }

    function request2filter( formRequest ){

        var filterFR = {};

        for (const property in formRequest) {
            switch( property ){
                case 'primaryCountries':
                    filterFR.countries = formRequest[property];
                break;
                case 'genres':
                    filterFR.genres = formRequest[property];
                break;
                case 'fromYear':
                    filterFR.years = [];
                    filterFR.years.push(formRequest[property]);
                break;
                case 'toYear':
                    filterFR.years.push(formRequest[property]);
                break;
                case 'runtimeMin':
                    filterFR.runtime = [];
                    if( formRequest[property] == null )
                        formRequest[property] = 0;
                    filterFR.runtime.push(decodeValueRuntime( formRequest.movieFilterForm, formRequest[property] ));
                break;
                case 'runtimeMax':

                    var runtimeDecode = decodeValueRuntime(formRequest.movieFilterForm, formRequest[property]);
                    if( typeof runtimeDecode == 'string')
                        if( runtimeDecode.startsWith('+') )
                            runtimeDecode = 1000;

                    filterFR.runtime.push( runtimeDecode );
                break;
                case 'minRatingCount':
                    minratCount = decodeValueRatCount(formRequest[property]);
                    filterFR.minRatingCount = minratCount;
                break;
                case 'movieFilterForm':
                    filterFR.movieFilterForm = formRequest[property];
                break;
                case 'platforms':
                    filterFR.platforms = formRequest[property];
                break;
                default:
                    console.log('default');
            }
        }

        return filterFR;
    }

    function convertValueRatCount( rating ){
        var ratings = ['20', '100', '500', '1000'];

        return ratings.indexOf( rating );
    }

    function convertValueRuntime( runtime ){
        var flagTypeSel = $('select[name="flags-type"]').val();
        var runtimes = flagsConfig[flagTypeSel].sliderruntime.ticks;
        var runtimeArray = runtime.split(',');

        return {'runtimeMin' : runtimes.indexOf( parseInt(runtimeArray[0]) ),
                'runtimeMax': runtimes.indexOf( parseInt(runtimeArray[1]) )};
    }

    function decodeValueRuntime( typeFilterForm, indexOfRuntime ){
        typeFilterForm = decodeURI(typeFilterForm);
        var flagTypeSel = typeFilterForm.split('|');
        var runtimes = flagsConfig[flagTypeSel[0]].sliderruntime.ticks;

        return runtimes[indexOfRuntime];
    }

    function decodeValueRatCount( indexOfRating ){
        var ratings = ['20', '100', '500', '1000'];

        return ratings[indexOfRating];
    }

    function changeFlagsType(flagType)
    {
        var row = $('.fframe .flags-content');

        if(typeof flagType == 'undefined')
        {
            flagType = 'full';
        }

        if( $('.genre-combo').find('.disabled') ){
            $('.genre-combo').find('.include').removeClass('include');
            $('.genre-combo').find('.active').removeClass('active');
            $('.genre-combo').find('.exclude').removeClass('exclude');
            $('.genre-combo').find('.disabled').removeClass('disabled');
        }

        loadFilterGenres();

        switch( flagType ){
            case 'movie':
                if( $('.genre-combo .dropdown-item[data-value="TV_SE"]').find('.active').length <= 0 )
                    $('.genre-combo .dropdown-item[data-value="TV_SE"]').addClass('disabled');

                if( $('.genre-combo .dropdown-item[data-value="DO"]').find('.active').length <= 0  )
                    $('.genre-combo .dropdown-item[data-value="DO"]').addClass('disabled');


                var facheckboxs = $('.flags-content div[data-flag="movie"] .btn-group').find('.fa-btn-checkbox');
                $(facheckboxs).each(function(indexFa, valueFa){
                    if( $(valueFa).hasClass('active') && $(valueFa).find('input').attr('data-option') == 'ex-anim' )
                        $('.genre-combo .dropdown-item[data-value="AN"]').addClass('disabled');
                })
            break;
            case 'serie':
                $('.genre-combo .dropdown-item[data-value="TV_SE"]').addClass('disabled');
                var facheckboxs = $('.flags-content div[data-flag="serie"] .btn-group').find('.fa-btn-checkbox');
                $(facheckboxs).each(function(indexFa, valueFa){
                    if( $(valueFa).hasClass('active') && $(valueFa).find('input').attr('data-option') == 'ex-anim' )
                        $('.genre-combo .dropdown-item[data-value="AN"]').addClass('disabled');
                })
            break;
            case 'documentary':
                $('.genre-combo .dropdown-item[data-value="DO"]').addClass('disabled');
            break;
            case 'animation':
                $('.genre-combo .dropdown-item[data-value="AN"]').addClass('disabled');
            break;
        }

        $('> div', row).hide();

        $('[data-flag="' + flagType + '"]', row).show();

        //$('.fframe [name="flags-type"]').val(flagType).selectpicker('refresh');

        //renderLegend();
        renderGenresLegend();
    }


    function changeSlider(flagType)
    {
        if(typeof flagType == 'undefined')
        {
            flagType = 'full';
        }

        $('#filter_top .flags-slider').find('.sliderruntime').slider('destroy');

        var lastEle = flagsConfig[flagType].sliderruntime.ticks.length - 1;

        $('#filter_top .flags-slider').find('.sliderruntime').slider({
            ticks: flagsConfig[flagType].sliderruntime.ticks,
            ticks_labels: flagsConfig[flagType].sliderruntime.labels,
            ticks_positions: flagsConfig[flagType].sliderruntime.positions,
            lock_to_ticks: true,
            range: true,
        }).slider('setValue', [0, flagsConfig[flagType].sliderruntime.ticks[lastEle] ]).slider('refresh',{ useCurrentValue: true });
    }

    function updatePlatformsValue()
    {
        let frame = $('.fframe');
        let platforms = new Array();

        $.each($('.platforms option:selected', frame), function(index, option)
        {
            platforms.push($(option).val());
        });

        $('[name="platforms"]', frame).val(platforms.join(','));
    }


    function loadFlags()
    {
        var row = $('.fframe .flags-content');
        for(flagType in flagsConfig)
        {
            flagsConfig[flagType].subfilters.forEach(function(groupData, index)
            {
                var groupDiv = $('[data-flag="' + flagType + '"]:eq(' + index + ')', row);

                $.each($('input', groupDiv), function(index, span)
                {
                    setFlag($(span), false);
                });

                groupData.defaults.forEach(function(option)
                {
                    var label = $('[data-option="' + option + '"]', groupDiv).closest('label');
                    setFlag(label, true);
                });

            });
        }
    }


    function loadFilter(filter)
    {
        var filterprocc = request2filter(filter);

        loadFlags();

        filterprocc.movieFilterForm = decodeURI(filterprocc.movieFilterForm);
        loadFilterFlags(filterprocc.movieFilterForm);

        loadFilterGenres(filterprocc.genres);

        loadFilterSliders(filterprocc);

        var frame = $('.fframe');

        if(filterprocc.countries)
        {
            $('[name="country"]', frame).selectpicker('val', filterprocc.countries);
        }
        else
        {
            $('#country').selectpicker('val', '');
        }

        if(filterprocc.platforms)
        {
            filterprocc.platforms.forEach(function(platformId)
            {
                $('.nav.nav-tabs li[data-prov-id="' + platformId + '"]').addClass('selected');
            });
        }
        else
        {
            $('.nav.nav-tabs li').removeClass('selected');
        }

        updatePlatformsValue();
    }

    function loadFilterFlags(filterFlags)
    {
        if(filterFlags)
        {
            var row = $('.fframe .flags-content');

            var parts = filterFlags.split('|');

            parts.forEach(function(part, i)
            {
                if(i > 0)
                {
                    var groupDiv = $('[data-flag="' + parts[0] + '"]:eq(' + (i-1) + ')', row);

                    $.each($('label', groupDiv), function(index, span)
                    {
                        setFlag($(span), false);
                    });


                    var options = part.split(':');

                    options.forEach(function(option)
                    {
                        var span = $('[data-option="' + option + '"]', groupDiv).closest('label');
                        $('input[data-option="' + option + '"]', groupDiv).prop('checked', true);

                        setFlag(span, true);
                    });
                }
            });

            $('[name="flags-type"]').selectpicker('val', parts[0]);
            changeFlagsType(parts[0]);
        }
        else
        {
            changeFlagsType();
        }
    }

    function disabledCheck( value ){
        $('.flags.flags-content label input[data-option="' + value + '"]').closest('label').removeClass('active').addClass('disabled');
    }


    function loadFilterGenres(genres)
    {
        let frame = $('.fframe');

        if(genres)
        {
            //genres = genres.split(',');
            genres.forEach(function(genre)
            {
                let label = $('.genre-combo [value="' + genre + '"]', this).closest('label');
                let labelText = $('.genre-combo [value="' + genre + '"]', this).closest('.btn-group-toggle').find('.text');
                setGenreCheck(label, true);
                setGenreState(labelText, genre);

                matches = genre.match(/AN/)
                if( matches != null )
                    disabledCheck('ex-anim');

                matches = '';
                matches = genre.match(/DO/)
                if( matches != null )
                    disabledCheck('ex-docu');

            }, frame);

            //renderLegend();
            renderGenresLegend();
        }
        else
        {
            $('.reset-combo', frame).trigger('click');
        }
    }


    function renderGenresLegend()
    {
        let frame = $('.fframe');
        let legend = $('.legend', frame);

        let genresBox = $('.genre-combo', frame);
        let button = $('.dropdown-toggle', frame);

        let includes = new Array();
        let excludes = new Array();

        $.each($('input:checked', genresBox), function(index, input)
        {
            let value = $(input).val();
            let genreName = $.trim($(input).closest('.btn-group').find('.text').text());

            if(value[0] == '+')
            {
                includes.push(genreName);
            }
            else
            {
                excludes.push(genreName);
            }
        });


        let text = '';

        if(includes.length > 0)
        {
            let includeText = $('.hidden-texts .include-genres', legend).clone();

            $('span', includeText).text(includes.join(', '));

            text += includeText.html();
        }
        if(excludes.length > 0)
        {
            let excludeText = $('.hidden-texts .exclude-genres', legend).clone();
            $('span', excludeText).text(excludes.join(', '));

            text += excludeText.html();
        }

        if(text == '')
        {
            text = $('.hidden-texts .any-genre', legend).text();
            button.addClass('empty');

        }
        else
        {
            button.removeClass('empty');
        }

        $('.genres-legend', genresBox).html(text);
        $('.dropdown-toggle', genresBox).html(text);

    }

    function getRatingCountVal()
    {
        var frame = $('.fframe form');
        var pos = $('[name="ratingcount"]', frame).val();

        return MIN_RATING_VALUES[pos];
    }


    function loadOffersPopover(button, movieId)
    {
        button.off('hover');

        button.popover({
            content: offersCache[movieId],
            html: true,
            container: button.closest('li'),
            title: offersTitle,

        }).popover('show');
    }

    $('.skeleton').fadeOut('slow', function() {
        $('.fframe .form-wrapper').fadeIn('slow', function(){
            $('.sliderratings').slider('relayout');
            $('.sliderruntime').slider('relayout');

            $('.nav-tabs').scrollingTabs({
                cssClassLeftArrow: 'fa fa-chevron-left',
                cssClassRightArrow: 'fa fa-chevron-right',
            });

            $('.platforms-wrapper').fadeIn();
        });
    });

    $('.nav.nav-tabs').on('click', 'a', function(e){
        e.preventDefault();
        if( $('.platforms-wrapper .nav.nav-tabs .selected').length < 10 ){
            $(this).closest('li').toggleClass('selected');
        } else {
            $(this).closest('li').removeClass('selected');
            if( $(this).closest('.platforms-wrapper').find('.subheader .in-block').length <= 0 )
                $(this).closest('.platforms-wrapper').find('.subheader').append('<div class="in-block"><small>'+ tcCommon.t('You can only choose 10 platforms')  +'</small></div>')
        }
    })

});
</script>

    </script>
</div>
